rows.label: qst003602_msg0001
rows.name:
Mopopo not working right now. But
what is friend's business?

rows.label: qst003602_msg0002
rows.name:
Oh... This is about friend Hula's
order...

rows.label: qst003602_msg0003
rows.name: Things she order right here.

rows.label: qst003602_msg0004
rows.name: But Mopopo not going to deliver.

rows.label: qst003602_msg0005
rows.name:
Since Morph go, not allowed to
charge extra fees for transporting
goods to Gula.

rows.label: qst003602_msg0006
rows.name: Militia Corps really quite strict.

rows.label: qst003602_msg0007
rows.name:
Once, Mopopo could make megafortune
just by making delivery to Gula.

rows.label: qst003602_msg0008
rows.name:
But not now. So Mopopo cannot be
bothered.

rows.label: qst003602_msg0009
rows.name: Did Hula ask friend to come here?

rows.label: qst003602_msg0010
rows.name:
Are you going back to place where
Hula is?

rows.label: qst003602_msg0011
rows.name: Okay. This how to fix.

rows.label: qst003602_msg0012
rows.name:
Friend can take goods to Gula
instead of Mopopo.

rows.label: qst003602_msg0013
rows.name:
Mopopo might not be working right
now, but head is still working. Pretty
impressive.

rows.label: qst003602_msg0014
rows.name:
Mopopo actually quite sad not to do
normal route. Usually always eat Tasty
Sausage when making delivery there.

rows.label: qst003602_msg0015
rows.name:
But no! Mopopo not do work
for such meager pay.

rows.label: qst003602_msg0016
rows.name:
Mopopo might take further orders
from Hula though, if price is right.
Please tell to Hula.

rows.label: qst003602_msg0017
rows.name: Okay. Mopopo leave it to you.

rows.label: qst003602_msg0101
rows.name:
Tasty Sausage...
Gulan Honeytea...
Ruska Dumplings...

rows.label: qst003602_msg0102
rows.name:
Mopopo too lazy to move for scant
reward. But still hanker after Gula
cuisine...

rows.label: qst003602_msg0103
rows.name:
If only some tasty treats would fall out
of sky...
